<plot>James Harris is arrested for the murder of his best friend Adrian Knight and sent to a medium security hospital for the mentally deranged. There, through strange dreams, he begins to piece together that fateful night and the truth behind it. With the aid of fellow inmates Bill Fischer and Rob McDonald, they formulate an escape plan so that Harris can finally bring closure and truth to light. Will Harris be freed before it's too late, or will he be sentenced to a life without bail?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?335659</url></doc>
